Name: Demonic Labyrinth
About the game: Demonic Labyrinth is an Action Roguelike with RPG elements. You find yourself in an endless closed labyrinth littered with a pile of earth and stones. To get out, you have to clear your way and look for the right solution. labyrinth, fighting off a crowd of undead, which has long been waiting for a victim. According to the rules of the maze, one broken block that hid the enemy breaks four blocks in the neighborhood and can create a whole chain that will clear the path for the hero, but and create a small undead army. Peculiarities: - Nice graphics. - Random level generation. - Pumping the main character.
